CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 18, reads: "An interesting photo of the 'Slams' (lower left) and some of their out of town guests. Mrs. Gladys Mehlinger of Washington, Atty. Eunice Hunton Carter of New York, Irene Trigg Perkins and Mary Kraft Cotterall, both of Washington, are the fine looking ladies seated on the front row.  Florence Lewis, Marjorie Levy, Susie McNeal, Julia Bumry Jones, Ada Walker and Bessie Kennedy, members on the second row.  in back are Jayne McDaniels and Agnes Stephenson also members of the Little Slams."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, front row from left: Gladys Mehlinger, Eunice Hunton Carter, Irene Trigg Perkins, Mary Kraft Cotterall; middle: Florence Lewis, Marjorie Levy, Susie McNeal, Julia Bumry Jones, Ada Walker, Bessie Kennedy; back: Jayne McDaniels, and Agnes Stephenson, posed in Loendi Club for Slams Club farm party
